<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to CALDOST</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 30px 0;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #1f2a44;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .email-body h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1f2a44;
    }

    .email-body p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .highlight-box {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f1f4f8;
      border-left: 4px solid #1f2a44;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .email-footer strong {
      color: #1f2a44;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #e5e7eb;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-container">

      <!-- HEADER -->
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>CALDOST</h1>
      </div>

      <!-- BODY -->
      <div class="email-body">
        <h2>Welcome, <%= name %></h2>

        <p>
          We’re pleased to inform you that your <strong>Super Admin account</strong>
          has been successfully created on <strong>CALDOST</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          You now have access to the administrative dashboard and system-level
          management features based on the permissions assigned to your account.
        </div>

        <p>
          You can log in using the credentials you provided during account setup.
          For security reasons, please ensure that your login details remain
          confidential at all times.
        </p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>
          If you did not request this account or believe this email was sent to you
          by mistake, please contact our support team immediately.
        </p>

        <p>
          We’re glad to have you on board and look forward to working with you.
        </p>

        <p>
          Regards,<br />
          <strong>CALDOST Team</strong><br />
          <span>www.caldost.com</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          This is an automated email from <strong>CALDOST</strong>.  
          Please do not reply to this message.
        </p>
        <p>
          © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> CALDOST. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
